{"tid":1623053,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"續。割蓆宣言","createTime":"2019-10-04T18:11:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T07:13:06.000Z","uid":175453,"like":116,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"a5fd987d239a21751505da8523f52b3ebcf437ef","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"有鑑於港共同狗隻對香港人既打壓無效<br />\n極有可能出現偽裝示威者以抺黑示威者之行為<br />\n因此<br />\n現正作出割蓆宣言<br />\n<br />\nThe movement has recently found the need for a declaration of discipline code upon common consensus have been reached. This declaration will minimise any possibility on act of sabotage and infiltration by the regime and ensure certain level of safety to the activity itself<br />\n<br />\n一，示威者不會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">惡意</span></span>傷害任何<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無辜</span></span>人士之性命財產。<br />\n<br />\nThe participant of the movement would not attack/penalise any innocent individual themself and their property<br />\n<br />\n二，示威者不強姦，不搶劫。<br />\n<br />\nThe participant of the movement would not commence any sexual indecent act such as raping or sexual assault nor any criminal act of robbing or related.<br />\n<br />\n三，示威者對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">報導事實</span></span>的記者，醫護，消防，外國朋友等一律表示尊重。<br />\n<br />\nThe participant of the movement would respect and protect individuals who is journalists with genuine purpose on reporting the truth , any medicals practitioners or any foreigner in need at all scene under any condition.<br />\n<br />\n四，示威者作出的一切行為皆對準<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共極權或任何助長港共極權之人士、團體和機構</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\nThe participant of the movement would only target on individuals/group who has been demonstrate behaviour that either involve in suppression of Hong Kong democracy or safety of the participant at scene.<br />\n<br />\n註：<br />\n<br />\n一，助長極權人士包括藍絲，紅店，絕對贊成召喚鶳/裝修。<br />\n<br />\n二，若行動理念一致，請盡量勿捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n賊仔例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z736wQV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ736wQV.jpg&h=9b151a97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請記住 示威者非罪犯 而係正義之師<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqbzFKu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqbzFKu.jpg&h=e6e0576d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家港共咩都做得出<br />\n要有共識<br />\n<br />\n附上手足整既文宣:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ha2bHZs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHa2bHZs.jpg&h=4c5fc369&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCFD7q9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCFD7q9.jpg&h=5985561c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上PO:<br />\n<br />\n割蓆宣言<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554029</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84335a7170ffbd33b5e53f4dd786dd3ec55b5c46","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:11:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29fc5d8618327c37deea4a3a2d98c079789bd32a","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:12:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f297d70534c84fb44a1c14e8d5af1d1752695349","tid":1623053,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:12:34.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"103c988a867ec4e1104404aa0d7490bac8ecf656","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20