y":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:16:10.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"fb7d0fa1e78a94c5ce6fd6199722e69a0d77935a","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"020d9fe9dc2b90dd026b41b55b3b5ab74265c51d","tid":1623053,"uid":147785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:15:23.000Z","msg":"推英文版上twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要再搵埋 民間記者會 講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:16:17.000Z","msg":"推呀 大家可能要幫手睇睇grammar"},{"pid":"c8dc40474c3301577f36a189eedba21a4a6f5fa2","tid":1623053,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:16:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">破解緊急法！</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">只有全民<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">無&middot;限&middot;期</span>罷工罷課先可以救自己、救香港！</span></strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610341\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610341</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">早前政府宣布，香港各區發生暴動！今日宣布立緊急法</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">亦即係話，當日只要出過街嘅非警察人士，都有機會告你參與暴動</span>！<span style=\"color: red;\">要去狗屋坐48個鐘，而且定罪嘅話一坐就幾年</span>！<br />\n<br />\n打工反學嘅你，為你自己將來，呼籲大家，<span style=\"color: red;\">盡快組織無限期罷工、罷課</span>！<span style=\"color: gold;\">只有咁，先可以癱瘓社會運作，直到政府宣布徹底妥協為止！</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n罷工，你可能面對被炒魷魚嘅風險，但罷工不需要附上刑責！警察唔可能上門捉你返工！<span style=\"color: red;\">只要齊心，換來嘅係政府徹底讓步！大家包括今日有出街嘅人亦唔會被告暴動！警察亦可以立即停止暴力，義士亦可以沉冤得雪</span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">如果大家唔齊心罷工，有一日警察會上門捉你，告你暴動！就算唔係，警察以後亦會變本加厲，用更重手對付大家！以後大家無機會出聲！</span>今日見到已經開槍謀殺義士！我地一定要立即制止納粹警暴歪風！請大家立即籌備無限期罷工、罷課！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong>請文宣幫手將以上論點製作poster廣傳，多謝各位</strong>"},{"pid":"819f3d7ceb15fdc666fe9e3743e0c45bca38b0aa","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:16:47.000Z","msg":"大大力"},{"pid":"6abdda608f503ffde50f274ac2b4b5eb4776529c","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:17:06.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"59fee889a580c26f937ee7c3c610c65d66dca893","tid":1623053,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:17:20.000Z","msg":"【行動核彈】你嘅幫手可以搞冧騰訊同埋新浪！強國人無得用微信微博，順便搞冧深圳<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1620007\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1620007</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e8ed96e27465244c8fced3ba6b6deb8c1a358558","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:17:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"68d92a7660dda85a8e5e2bec89d2a3dc39a4381a","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:18:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a49038a495457c992a71d39055a686b0a61b9561","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:19:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51036efc00203adec14019c7328bd72990ffa4e2","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:20:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22d5f779b7ddaf972dd181a025aa6ee71d39da26","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:21:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0d48266b767cc2eefa11907ffce19bf281863640","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:21:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e4cb168f4fca8dde4fcbe178bdd869b1f45dce42","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:22:32.000Z","msg":"頂"},{"pid":"fad8ea502a36e34391da204f93b84c63d62b3053","tid":1623053,"uid":200087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:23:15.000Z","msg":"宣言之餘，都要行動。見到有人偷就要阻止。"},{"pid":"1cb034a76a8920e2b441aba41b630d9ec155ba32","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fad8ea502a36e34391da204f93b84c63d62b3053",