replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:15:22.000Z","msg":"我地唔係賊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"我地係為自由而戰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:45:29.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔裝到藍店 佢地有發言既自由 除非做左啲咩害到手足 唔係既話應該只針對紅底既鋪頭 <br />\n<br />\n大家都識講 黃藍是政見 唔可以因為佢反對你就打佢 除非佢手出左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a8245810fb9b8e03cf34ffa1d8e08ae48113d0","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:45:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a028cdf692a6ca08a316f903083a28197933504","tid":1623053,"uid":256620,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a5fd987d239a21751505da8523f52b3ebcf437ef","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:11:03.000Z","msg":"有鑑於港共同狗隻對香港人既打壓無效<br />\n極有可能出現偽裝示威者以抺黑示威者之行為<br />\n因此<br />\n現正作出割蓆宣言<br />\n<br />\nThe movement has recently found the need for a declaration of discipline code upon common consensus have been reached. This declaration will minimise any possibility on act of sabotage and infiltration by the regime and ensure certain level of safety to the activity itself<br />\n<br />\n一，示威者不會<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">惡意</span></span>傷害任何<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">無辜</span></span>人士之性命財產。<br />\n<br />\nThe participant of the movement would not attack/penalise any innocent individual themself and their property<br />\n<br />\n二，示威者不強姦，不搶劫。<br />\n<br />\nThe participant of the movement would not commence any sexual indecent act such as raping or sexual assault nor any criminal act of robbing or related.<br />\n<br />\n三，示威者對<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">報導事實</span></span>的記者，醫護，消防，外國朋友等一律表示尊重。<br />\n<br />\nThe participant of the movement would respect and protect individuals who is journalists with genuine purpose on reporting the truth , any medicals practitioners or any foreigner in need at all scene under any condition.<br />\n<br />\n四，示威者作出的一切行為皆對準<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">港共極權或任何助長港共極權之人士、團體和機構</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\nThe participant of the movement would only target on individuals/group who has been demonstrate behaviour that either involve in suppression of Hong Kong democracy or safety of the participant at scene.<br />\n<br />\n註：<br />\n<br />\n一，助長極權人士包括藍絲，紅店，絕對贊成召喚鶳/裝修。<br />\n<br />\n二，若行動理念一致，請盡量勿捉鬼<br />\n<br />\n賊仔例子：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z736wQV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ736wQV.jpg&h=9b151a97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n請記住 示威者非罪犯 而係正義之師<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PqbzFKu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPqbzFKu.jpg&h=e6e0576d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請幫手推上熱門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />依家港共咩都做得出<br />\n要有共識<br />\n<br />\n附上手足整既文宣:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ha2bHZs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHa2bHZs.jpg&h=4c5fc369&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WCFD7q9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWCFD7q9.jpg&h=5985561c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上PO:<br />\n<br />\n割蓆宣言<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1554029\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1554029</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:46:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1623065/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1623065/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n請停止攻擊多貴重物品既商鋪 如中移動電話鋪<br />\n頭先ssp有人爆中移動電話舖<br />\n一班南亞stand by緊偷iphone 11<br />\n再爆就會有人笠撚住個頭跟住爆金鋪錶鋪/爆入銀行搶錢<br />\n偷晒d嘢再入鳩大家數<br />\nd狗仲可以名正言順用實彈打搶劫金鋪/銀行既劫匪<br />\n咁落去只會引黎一班臥底狗 同南亞小偷混入現場示威者到處破壞店舖<br />\n然後有人唔同意/混亂之際 <br />\n就會發生打群架&gt;你分唔人同狗&gt;狗隻裹應外合 突擊圍捕&gt;入鳩你搶掠"},{"pid":"2e5456e92b86b7ba32cd68d17b9571663afd16e8","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"201d87f9f5ce97f4c837d3ec1c60b3f24a48c19e","tid":1623053,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79253a442e1287ff1386af0d1bede482c6a84d17","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fa9e9a7e04c5f74f0f168d7275a0ccf3de793fa3","tid":1623053,"uid":142904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:15:22.000Z","msg":"我地唔係賊仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"我地係為自由而戰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:45:29.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔裝到藍店 佢地有發言既自由 除非做左啲咩害到手足 唔係既話應該只針對紅底既鋪頭 <br />\n<br />\n大家都識講 黃藍是政見 唔可以因為佢反對你就打佢 除非佢手出左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:47:24.000Z","msg":"呢個 裝修藍店唔割"},{"pid":"e8ae12fee7fd67c7ae8a3b9f50796ea0625d2f8a","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:48:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2be65fa34c38784a1377dc47abaeac035d554caf","tid":1623053,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2e5456e92b86b7ba32cd68d17b9571663afd16e8","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"201d87f9f5ce97f4c837d3ec1c60b3f24a48c19e","tid":1623053,"uid":15362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79253a442e1287ff1386af0d1bede482c6a84d17","tid":1623053,"uid":175453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:15:45.000Z","msg":"我地係為自由而戰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:45:29.000Z","msg":"可唔可以唔裝到藍店 佢地有發言既自由 除非做左啲咩害到手足 唔係既話應該只針對紅底既鋪頭 <br />\n<br />\n大家都識講 黃藍是政見 唔可以因為佢反對你就打佢 除非佢手出左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit